-- Stocks Pare Decline in Europe as Mining Shares Rally; U.S. Futures Advance
-- Andrew Rummer
-- 2010-07-19T09:03:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/stocks-erase-decline-in-europe-as-mining-shares-rally-u-s-futures-climb.html

          
          
             European stocks erased their decline
as basic-resources producers and technology companies advanced.
The Stoxx Europe 600 Index rose less than 0.1 percent to 248.3
at 10:02 a.m. in London, having earlier lost as much as 0.8
percent.  
          
          


  


        